{
  "page": "Trios",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Trios</b>, or <b>Three-Headed Trios</b>, is a three-headed god worshipped in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. There is a large statue of him by the doors of the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_Trios\" title=\"Temple of Trios\">Temple of Trios</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> There is also a tower with three turrets dedicated to Trios in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Trios&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Trios&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> that a <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf\" title=\"Dwarf\">dwarf</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Dwarf_juggler\" title=\"Dwarf juggler\">juggler</a> that she and her brother <a href=\"/index.php/Oppo\" title=\"Oppo\">Oppo</a> knew had been found murdered and dismembered at the <a href=\"/index.php/Temple_of_Trios\" title=\"Temple of Trios\">Temple of Trios</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a>. He had been cut into three parts, each part placed into one of the three mouths of the statue of Trios. However, when the parts were put back together, the juggler's head was missing. Penny and Tyrion feel certain that the dwarf's head was taken to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> for Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a>, who has put a bounty on Tyrion's head.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Sailor%27s_Wife\" title=\"Sailor&#39;s Wife\">Sailor's Wife</a> once told <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> that the first head of Trio devours the dying and the reborn emerge from the third, but she did not recall the purpose of the middle head.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Trios&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_64\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 64\">Chapter 64</a>, The Ugly Little Girl.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404204528\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 453/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8650/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1476/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 88/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1558/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.566      1 -total\n 82.25%   10.336      4 Template:Ref\n 52.68%    6.620      4 Template:Ref/core\n 15.06%    1.893      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:17950-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404204528 and revision id 324638\n -->\n",
